1
00:01:05,439 --> 00:01:05,840
Right.

2
00:01:06,319 --> 00:01:06,959
It's him.

3
00:01:07,319 --> 00:01:08,200
I was wondering.

4
00:01:08,599 --> 00:01:10,280
They don't look alike at all.

5
00:01:10,280 --> 00:01:11,680
How could they be relatives?

6
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,239
Yet he came to pick her up every day.

7
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:15,920
He actually kidnapped Wen Jie's sister to threaten him.

8
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,200
Then Wen Jie getting arrested...

9
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,680
Was he also framed by Zhou Honghai?

10
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:20,000
Without solid evidence,

11
00:01:20,159 --> 00:01:21,120
let's not jump to conclusions yet.

12
00:01:23,400 --> 00:01:24,200
Hello?

13
00:01:25,239 --> 00:01:26,159
Okay.

14
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:28,959
The little girl has been found.

15
00:01:29,200 --> 00:01:30,519
Near the bus terminal.

16
00:01:31,040 --> 00:01:32,519
But the suspect, Zhou Honghai,

17
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:34,159
must have realized he was being watched.

18
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:36,239
He abandoned the girl and ran.

19
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,519
How is the sister doing now?

20
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,879
The girl isn't in good shape.

21
00:01:40,120 --> 00:01:41,959
But she said Zhou Honghai threatened her.

22
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:43,280
If she didn't listen,

23
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:44,560
he would hurt her brother.

24
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,319
With her testimony,

25
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:48,079
there's a chance to clear Wen Jie's name.

26
00:01:49,840 --> 00:01:51,840
Although the Long Group abandoned Zhou Honghai,

27
00:01:51,959 --> 00:01:52,680
at the time of the incident,

28
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,920
Wen Jie was still with them.

29
00:01:54,439 --> 00:01:55,239
I'm worried

30
00:01:55,640 --> 00:01:57,280
the Long Group won't let the case be overturned so easily.

31
00:01:58,120 --> 00:01:58,959
Let's go to the law firm.

32
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,080
This is it.

33
00:02:08,599 --> 00:02:09,759
It happened right here in my last life.

34
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,360
You wait here.

35
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,080
I'll go over by myself.

36
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:12,759
No.

37
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,680
Didn't we agree to do this together?

38
00:02:15,080 --> 00:02:15,759
Besides,

39
00:02:16,319 --> 00:02:17,360
the nightmare is over.

40
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:22,039
Where's yours?

41
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,199
I probably left it at home in the rush.

42
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:24,800
Let's go.

43
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,199
Chen Fan.

44
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:31,240
Hello. Half an hour ago,

45
00:03:31,240 --> 00:03:32,360
a girl from the Hubin Road accident named

46
00:03:32,360 --> 00:03:33,319
Su Ruochu.

47
00:03:33,319 --> 00:03:34,520
Where is she? How is she doing?

48
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:36,520
She was just moved from the ER to the observation ward.

49
00:03:36,599 --> 00:03:37,240
Go straight inside.

50
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,039
Ruochu, you scared me to death.

51
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:47,240
Where is Chen Fan?

52
00:03:48,840 --> 00:03:49,639
Where is Chen Fan?

53
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:50,960
Doctor.

54
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,639
How is my friend doing?

55
00:03:53,639 --> 00:03:54,520
She's going to be fine.

56
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:57,120
Soft tissue contusions from the impact of the crash.

57
00:03:57,120 --> 00:03:58,319
Minor hairline fracture in the ribs.

58
00:03:58,560 --> 00:03:59,400
Scalp bleeding.

59
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,639
A mild concussion.

60
00:04:01,039 --> 00:04:02,039
Brief loss of consciousness.

61
00:04:02,319 --> 00:04:03,759
She needs to be hospitalized for 48 hours of observation.

62
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:05,319
We'll do a dynamic head CT scan.

63
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:07,159
To rule out delayed intracranial hemorrhage.

64
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:08,199
Get some rest.

65
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,080
Oh my god.

66
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,479
That sounds so scary.

67
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:12,319
Ruochu, take your time.

68
00:04:12,479 --> 00:04:13,840
What exactly happened?

69
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,839
We were just about to cross the street.

70
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:20,959
We were heading to the law firm across the street.

71
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:23,399
Then a car suddenly rushed towards us.

72
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:25,639
I was hit before I could even react.

73
00:04:25,839 --> 00:04:28,560
I almost thought this was like last time.

74
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,639
But last time, I was the one who got hit.

75
00:04:31,639 --> 00:04:33,199
Chen Fan was holding me back then.

76
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,600
But why is it him this time?

77
00:04:38,279 --> 00:04:40,600
Later, before I passed out...

78
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:42,959
I saw Chen Fan being dragged away.

79
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,439
Then when I woke up again,

80
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:45,959
I was already in the ambulance.

81
00:04:48,959 --> 00:04:50,360
Are you friends of the injured?

82
00:04:50,600 --> 00:04:50,959
Yes.

83
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:52,160
She was at No. 8 Binhu Road,

84
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,439
outside a law firm,

85
00:04:53,439 --> 00:04:54,199
when the accident happened.

86
00:04:54,879 --> 00:04:56,480
A lawyer from that firm called the police.

87
00:04:56,800 --> 00:04:58,240
When the rescue team arrived at the scene,

88
00:04:58,519 --> 00:04:59,680
she was the only one there.

89
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:01,319
Miss,

90
00:05:01,839 --> 00:05:02,519
do you remember

91
00:05:02,519 --> 00:05:04,519
what the car looked like or the license plate?

92
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,319
I can't remember clearly.

93
00:05:08,839 --> 00:05:10,279
It must be Zhou Honghai again.

94
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:10,879
Don't worry.

95
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,879
Our men have already sealed off the scene.

96
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,040
We are starting the investigation.

97
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,199
If there are any new findings,

98
00:05:15,199 --> 00:05:16,279
I will notify you immediately.

99
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:18,360
Okay.

100
00:05:22,879 --> 00:05:23,519
Brother Liang.

101
00:05:23,879 --> 00:05:25,160
I came as soon as I got your call.

102
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,120
Sister-in-law.

103
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,199
How did you get like this?

104
00:05:28,800 --> 00:05:29,480
Where is Brother Fan?

105
00:05:29,959 --> 00:05:30,879
It's all my fault.

106
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:32,399
If...

107
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,360
I hadn't let him come with me...

108
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,720
If I had stopped him...

109
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,240
he wouldn't be in trouble.

110
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,120
Don't panic yet.

111
00:05:40,079 --> 00:05:41,959
It hasn't reached the worst-case scenario yet.

112
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:44,800
I remember Brother Fan installed many cameras there.

113
00:05:45,399 --> 00:05:46,360
They must have captured evidence.

114
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:47,839
Take good care of Ruochu.

115
00:05:48,639 --> 00:05:49,319
I'll go check the surveillance footage.

116
00:05:49,680 --> 00:05:50,480
As long as we can prove his guilt,

117
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:51,480
we will definitely catch him.

118
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:54,319
Then I'll go with you.

119
00:05:57,360 --> 00:05:58,680
Don't cry, Ruochu.

120
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:01,759
It's going to be okay.

121
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:26,879
It really is you.

122
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:30,040
You're awake.

123
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:34,199
I wanted to find a quiet place to chat with you.

124
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:35,319
It really wasn't easy.

125
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,040
I don't feel like there's anything to talk about.

126
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,240
Don't be like that.

127
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:42,360
We have plenty to talk about.

128
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,680
For instance.

129
00:06:44,720 --> 00:06:46,920
Why are you always fixated on me?

130
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:49,279
Luo Wenjie's case was already settled.

131
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:50,079
Besides.

132
00:06:50,279 --> 00:06:51,920
I didn't really do anything to that little girl.

133
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:55,399
You kidnapped Wen Jie's sister to force him to take the blame.

134
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,839
Everything he did before...

135
00:06:57,839 --> 00:06:59,519
...was instigated by you, right?

136
00:07:01,639 --> 00:07:03,000
Luo Wenjie...

137
00:07:04,879 --> 00:07:06,279
All I did was occasionally...

138
00:07:06,279 --> 00:07:08,120
...take a couple of photos of his sister.

139
00:07:08,519 --> 00:07:10,439
And he was dead set on taking the fall for me.

140
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:13,560
Why do this?

141
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:16,040
It was for you, of course.

142
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,560
I wanted to start with him...

143
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,560
...and bring down everyone around you.

144
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,879
To let everyone know that following you, Chen Fan...

145
00:07:23,639 --> 00:07:24,839
...means no good life.

146
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,959
How did I offend you?

147
00:07:30,199 --> 00:07:32,800
Just you being alive annoys me.

148
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:34,240
Look how successful you are.

149
00:07:34,519 --> 00:07:35,839
You succeeded with websites.

150
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:37,000
Your internet cafes are a hit.

151
00:07:37,000 --> 00:07:37,839
You make hit games.

152
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:39,040
You sell antivirus software.

153
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:41,839
Why is it always smooth sailing for you?

154
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,600
Even Ruochu...

155
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:46,519
Even Ruochu follows you with all her heart.

156
00:07:46,519 --> 00:07:47,639
Why?

157
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:51,759
Aren't you just a lousy high school classmate?

158
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:54,120
I'm the one who actually likes her.

159
00:07:54,120 --> 00:07:56,319
You have the nerve to say you like her?

160
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:58,319
Last time during the crash, she went to persuade you.

161
00:07:58,319 --> 00:07:59,800
And you tried to kill her.

162
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,759
I didn't want to kill her last time.

163
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:06,839
I just wanted to get the evidence from her.

164
00:08:07,279 --> 00:08:07,959
It was the Long Group...

165
00:08:09,079 --> 00:08:09,560
Forget it.

166
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,120
Forget it, I've figured it out now.

167
00:08:11,519 --> 00:08:12,639
You are the one...

168
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:14,079
What exactly do you want?

169
00:08:14,079 --> 00:08:15,199
...who deserves to die the most.

170
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,040
Don't move.

171
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:20,839
Or I'll kill you.

172
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,439
I'm tired.

173
00:08:25,199 --> 00:08:27,079
I'll give you whatever you want.

174
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:29,920
My money, my properties.

175
00:08:30,879 --> 00:08:32,039
My game patents.

176
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,159
I'll give it all to you.

177
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,159
Except Ruochu.

178
00:08:37,559 --> 00:08:39,320
Do I look like I need your stuff?

179
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:44,600
What I want is the look Su Ruochu gives you.

180
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:14,799
No.

181
00:09:15,600 --> 00:09:17,159
I must find that red string.

182
00:09:18,480 --> 00:09:19,519
With it here...

183
00:09:19,919 --> 00:09:21,320
...Chen Fan will be safe.

184
00:09:57,639 --> 00:09:58,240
Ruochu.

185
00:09:58,639 --> 00:10:00,279
Actually, I've been waiting for this day.

186
00:10:01,000 --> 00:10:03,000
To tell you everything without reservation.

187
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:05,320
You once said that before the college entrance exam...

188
00:10:05,559 --> 00:10:06,600
...I seemed like a different person.

189
00:10:07,039 --> 00:10:08,039
Desperately making money.

190
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:09,440
Building websites, opening internet cafes.

191
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:10,919
Running clubs, making software.

192
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,960
As if I had endless energy.

193
00:10:14,039 --> 00:10:14,960
But do you know?

194
00:10:15,440 --> 00:10:16,399
I was just afraid.

195
00:10:17,720 --> 00:10:19,919
Afraid that another car would speed by one day.

196
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,799
And I could only watch helplessly as you fell under the wheels.

197
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:25,039
Without even a chance to reach out.

198
00:10:26,440 --> 00:10:27,519
The red string you gave me...

199
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:29,559
...I've been wearing it all along.

200
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:31,720
Our fate across two lifetimes...

201
00:10:32,519 --> 00:10:34,080
...is not something anyone can easily tear apart.

202
00:10:35,720 --> 00:10:36,639
We need to...

203
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,960
...tie it even tighter together.

204
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:41,519
As long as we are together...

205
00:10:41,679 --> 00:10:42,879
...there is nothing to fear.

206
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,320
I'm here.

207
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:47,039
More importantly...

208
00:10:48,240 --> 00:10:49,879
You have always been...

209
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,519
...much stronger than you think.
